description.en: ChickenSwap is completely distinguishable from the existing DEX’s on the market. While adopting the brilliant model of automatic market maker (AMM) and staking mining mechanism from Sushiswap , ChickenSwap is a more simplified, fair, secure, and profitable version of SUSHI that will launch in multiple phases to ensure sustainability.
